{"embedding_id": "chunk_0", "text": "# 课程知识点：AI Agent 基础\n\nAgent 是能围绕目标执行任务的智能系统。它通常包含：\n- 任务理解\n- 工具调用\n- 知识检索\n- 状态记录\n- 输出生成\n\nRAG 是一种让模型基于外部知识库回答问题的方法，能降低幻觉风险。", "asset_type": "chunk", "source_path": "examples/demo_education_tutor_agent/input/001_knowledge_points.md", "chunk_id": "08e7911ab19cc8dafe651842", "citation": "examples/demo_education_tutor_agent/input/001_knowledge_points.md#chunk=08e7911ab19cc8dafe651842", "title": "课程知识点：AI Agent 基础", "metadata": {}, "quality_score": 100, "created_at": "2026-06-03T12:16:44.120014+00:00"}
{"embedding_id": "chunk_1", "text": "# 错题讲解\n\n问题：为什么 RAG 可以降低幻觉？\n错误回答：因为 RAG 让模型变得更聪明。\n\n正确解释：\nRAG 通过检索外部知识库，把相关资料提供给模型，使回答更依赖可追溯资料，而不是只依赖模型参数记忆。", "asset_type": "chunk", "source_path": "examples/demo_education_tutor_agent/input/002_mistake_explanation.md", "chunk_id": "ffd4e24448d0259f08b1e9a8", "citation": "examples/demo_education_tutor_agent/input/002_mistake_explanation.md#chunk=ffd4e24448d0259f08b1e9a8", "title": "错题讲解", "metadata": {}, "quality_score": 100, "created_at": "2026-06-03T12:16:44.120014+00:00"}
{"embedding_id": "chunk_2", "text": "# 学习路径\n\n第一步：理解 Agent 和 RAG 的基本概念。\n第二步：学习知识库如何切分、清洗和评估。\n第三步：学习如何把知识库接入检索系统。\n第四步：学习如何为不同业务场景设计 Agent Template。", "asset_type": "chunk", "source_path": "examples/demo_education_tutor_agent/input/003_learning_path.md", "chunk_id": "abfaaf155270d0f8759fcfa7", "citation": "examples/demo_education_tutor_agent/input/003_learning_path.md#chunk=abfaaf155270d0f8759fcfa7", "title": "学习路径", "metadata": {}, "quality_score": 100, "created_at": "2026-06-03T12:16:44.120014+00:00"}
